      "turn_index": 220,
      "start_seconds": 7050330,
      "timestamp_label": "1958:25:30",
      "transcript_text": "And I hate to ask for data that I didn't previously ask you to prepare, but I'm just curious if there is just historic knowledge of sort of the, for lack of a better word, sort of restaurant migration sort of behavior historically when there have been changes in the meals tax. I might not be recalling this accurately, but I believe that there was sort of some landscape.",
