      "timestamp_label": "1303:15:53",
      "transcript_text": "Just one more follow-up question, also in response to something that was raised during the public hearing, um, and either for the City Attorney or Police Department, um, if you could comment on how enforcement works after hours Uh, you know, when the zoning inspector is, uh, not the one doing it, um, and how that might change or might stay the same going forward, or, you know, whatever, um, you have to share on that.",
