      "start_seconds": 5506739,
      "timestamp_label": "1529:38:59",
      "transcript_text": "Thank you, Mayor, Council. Tonight we have Davenport, specifically Mr. Lux and Mr. Sachs, who will be presenting two of the three presentations. Of the presentations, one will deal with the general fund FY27 plan of finance, specifically on capital. The other one will be on wastewater fund analysis, and the third one will be on the stormwater utility update as well. Um, happy to answer any questions during those presentations or any time after those presentations as well. Again, we have Kyle Lux from Davenport, with the city having a 25-year relationship with Davenport, who have really walked us through the financing. Also, they were a part of the city when we were upgraded from our AA to our AAA bond ratings as well. So So with that being said, we'll pull up the presentations and I'll turn it over to Mr. Laux.",
