      "transcript_text": "[Speaker:COMMISSIONER MILLER] Thank you. Very helpful. My next question is, I think, slide 11, and two different types of bonds here. The comment I think you made was along the lines of needing to identify a source of payments for those. There are two different types of bonds here that are referenced, general obligation and public facility revenue bonds. I'm curious to know how far along we are at actually identifying a source of repayments for the public facility revenue bonds and to understand that mechanism maybe a little bit more clearly also in contrast to the general obligation fund?",
