      "start_seconds": 14449394,
      "timestamp_label": "4013:43:14",
      "transcript_text": "So if I understand where we're landing here, it's for the city manager to come back with a suggestion on how we might proceed. Is that fair?",
      "snippet": "So if I understand where we're landing here, it's for the city manager to come back with a suggestion on how we might proceed. Is that fair?"
