      "timestamp_label": "4072:07:46",
      "transcript_text": "No, I appreciate that. Something to think about. Maybe is using some of that content for whatever we do on the open house or whatever we are going to call it, right? And be responsive to some of that. That way staff is not trying to weed through additional work that they have already responded to. What I would encourage, and I think we may have said that this via messaging back to you, is if there are items that we respond back to folks on, I think they are certainly fair game for for the context of the discussions we're having here. So I welcome you bringing some of those back that you see, because you're getting copied on everything we're sending back to them. So that's an opportunity I think also. So we'll pick through that a little bit. I'm sure that you probably have something to add to that, but we can reference a lot of that information as kind of, you know, content and context for this discussion that we've plan to have.",
