      "turn_index": 447,
      "start_seconds": 14987219,
      "timestamp_label": "4163:06:59",
      "transcript_text": "Miss Shinnaberry, it's going to be a discussion of a possible increase in the compensation and perenn salaries paid to the mayor and members of the city council. I'm going to recognize Brian Lokeman, our city attorney, to provide the staff report.",
