      "transcript_text": "Good evening. I would like to call the regular meeting of February 24th, 2026 to order. It's great to see everyone here tonight. I love a full house, or mostly a full house. There's nothing like government where everyone participates. If you are able and so choose, please rise for the Pledge of Allegiance. I pledge allegiance to the flag of the United States of America. And to the Republic for which it stands, one nation under God, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all. Right. I would like to ask Sophia Chapin, our stewardship coordinator, Urban Forest— Urban Forestry Forest Rescues Program Manager and Fairfax PRISM to come down for our National Invasive Species Awareness Week proclamation.",
