      "start_seconds": 4491344,
      "timestamp_label": "1247:35:44",
      "transcript_text": "Miss Shinneberry, our first item is a presentation by Police and Human Services on a coordinated community response I'm going to recognize Chief Pedroso to provide the staff presentation.",
