      "transcript_text": "So I should— this will be— this is a proprietary model. Provided to the city, uh, with under license agreements. So staff will have access to it. It will not be publicly available. This is our, uh, uh, you know, our, uh, Tischler Bice's proprietary, um, uh, property is our intellectual property.",
      "snippet": "So I should— this will be— this is a proprietary model. Provided to the city, uh, with under license agreements. So staff will have access to it. It will not be publicly available. This is our, uh, uh, you know, our, uh…"
