      "transcript_text": "Okay. And, and to your question too on the capital-operating distinction, so some of those other jurisdictions that I showed, uh, with other or similar models, those are complete models with operating and capital impacts as well. So we do fiscal models that, you know, that cover the operating impact of a new fire station because it's, you know, the fire— that's going to be the 15% of the full cost, 85% is going to be the ongoing operations and the shift that is associated with the apparatus. So, but that is part of our core services as well.",
