      "timestamp_label": "3133:21:06",
      "transcript_text": "My question is quick. In the introduction, you talked about us not having, um, policy guidance, so maybe you can just briefly talk about how this might inform policy guidance.",
      "snippet": "My question is quick. In the introduction, you talked about us not having, um, policy guidance, so maybe you can just briefly talk about how this might inform policy guidance."
