      "transcript_text": "Thank you much. Thank you very much for the presentation. Um, I was not fully aware of a lot of this information, so it's very helpful because it's not one of the boards I sit on, clearly. So I understand from the staff report that we're going to be asked later on to approve and move forward with this without knowing what our potential share of the $430 million will be. Is there an expectation of what that number will be?",
