      "transcript_text": "Uh, I have a clarifying question on the noise item. It's been an active month Mr. Mayor, thank you for noise. And I know there have been a number of things that have come up related to this. One of them is the issue of snow blowers. Another, we have heard a lot of comments about tonight, which is kind of this intersection between transportation and noise. I wonder if you could just help us sort of understand how to understand the current ordinance proposal that we have and what may have changed. Changed since the last time we spoke about this?",
