      "transcript_text": "Council Member McQuillan. Aye. Council Member Bates. Aye. Councilmember Peterson. Aye. Councilmember Hardy Chandler. Aye. Councilmember Hall. Aye. Councilmember Ammons. Aye. Motion passed unanimously. We will go to public hearing. We only have one public hearing tonight, which is a public hearing and council action on the adoption of the Urban Forest Master Plan, EMPRINS UFMP. I'm going to recognize Anna Stafford, Urban Forester, to provide the staff presentation.",
