      "start_seconds": 15017860,
      "timestamp_label": "4171:37:40",
      "transcript_text": "Miss Shinneberry, our last work session item for the night is an update and discussion on the joint city and county redevelopment of the Sherwood Community Center and Willard Health Center complex. I'm going to recognize Brooke Harden, our Community Development Director, to provide the staff presentation. Thank you.",
