      "turn_index": 298,
      "start_seconds": 18438204,
      "timestamp_label": "5121:43:24",
      "transcript_text": "So I think we have some public health representatives from the City of Fairfax here. I'm sorry we have kept— or from Fairfax County, rather. I am so sorry that we've kept you up so late. So I want to go back just for clarity and understand maybe the scope of services. For the health side of this. And again, appreciate so much that you're here. I think I heard earlier that the intention was that this was going to be focused on preventive care. Can I just understand a little bit more clearly about that? The reason I'm asking is I have heard from members of the community and I've since taken a look, and this can all be very flawed information. My understanding that this will have a tuberculosis center, and that would be designed to, um, engage in preventive care but also treatment. Is that correct?",
      "snippet": "So I think we have some public health representatives from the City of Fairfax here. I'm sorry we have kept— or from Fairfax County, rather. I am so sorry that we've kept you up so late. So I want to go back just for cl…"
