      "transcript_text": "Councilmember Amos. Stay awake, everyone, we're almost there. Uh, I only had a couple questions and then, uh, circle back. I'll just have a few comments, uh, no need to drag it out. Um, just to go more into that cost reduction slide, and I'm just more so curious about what your thought process was on that. How did we get to those specific changes and make those determinations? Oh, the savings?",
      "snippet": "Councilmember Amos. Stay awake, everyone, we're almost there. Uh, I only had a couple questions and then, uh, circle back. I'll just have a few comments, uh, no need to drag it out. Um, just to go more into that cost re…"
