      "timestamp_label": "2661:05:56",
      "transcript_text": "There's a lot of transition going on. Um, thank you. Uh, thank you, Mayor Reed and members of the council. Um, so tonight we have a presentation for you to go over and provide an overview of the Solid Waste Management Plan update in accordance with the Virginia Department of Environmental Quality, as well as open up for discussion to get your thoughts and feedback on the plan itself and a few key areas. I'm joined tonight by our consultant from RRS. We have Helen Lee and Olivia Polamini, um, who will also be helping with the presentation tonight.",
