      "transcript_text": "No, thank you for the presentation. This was great. I had two questions. One of them you kind of partially answered already, uh, because I was curious about what would happen if we just did the dwell time fee without the charging fee, what the discrepancy would be in the budget between revenues and costs. Uh, you kind of got into that, that you expect the dual fees to be lower because of increased parking enforcement. So I, I appreciate that, but maybe having those numbers would be helpful just for calculation. I'm curious about it because theoretically I— and maybe I shouldn't be thinking about it along the same terms of how I think about like the Q Bus system Are you concerned at all that this putting— increasing this fee or putting in this fee would deter folks from using the public EV charging?",
