      "transcript_text": "Just a general question. The ratio of engineering to construction on cost, this is a relatively small project and so the ratio, about a third of this is engineering and two-thirds construction as I see it. Is that pretty typical for this size class and does that stretch— how much— how does that stretch across other size classes?",
