      "transcript_text": "Councilmember Hardy Chandler? Aye. Councilmember Hall? Aye. Councilmember Amos? Aye. Motion passed unanimously. We'll Go to the next public hearing, which is a public hearing and council action on an ordinance amending Chapter 2, in parentheses, Administration, Article 3, in parentheses, Officers and Employees, Division 2, in parentheses, Disclosure of Interest, pertaining to required financial disclosures by certain enumerated officers and employees of the city. I'll recognize Brian Lubkeman, the City Attorney, to provide the staff report.",
