      "transcript_text": "Good evening, I'm Jim Gillespie. I reside at 3604 Colony Road. I'm here tonight to support the supplemental appropriation and moving ahead with the trail. I'm particularly excited about the connection with the cross-county trail. And the opportunity for, for residents of the county and the city to use that trail and actually to bring some business here within the city as well. I trust that the project planners and the city staff have worked diligently to preserve as many mature trees as possible, and I also trust that they will continue to do so as the project moves ahead. Thank you.",
