      "start_seconds": 4279690,
      "timestamp_label": "1188:48:10",
      "transcript_text": "Good evening, my name is Frank Shortella. I live at 3222 Cambridge Court, and this is the first time I'm speaking. Uh, I'm speaking on the George Snyder Trail transportation project. I'm opposed to building this road through old-growth forest because there are other better and cheaper alternatives available. Months ago, I presented a detailed plan for these alternatives, and I have received no response. I'm asking each and every one of you to please make the right decision and to save our woods. And I took the liberty of bringing one with— if I can give it to this young lady. If that would be all right. Thank you so much.",
